dotfiles
============

This is my personal dotfiles repository, containing configurations for Neovim,
Tmux, and other tools I use daily for software development.

Overview:
In this repository, you'll find configuration files tailored to optimize my
development environment. These dotfiles are designed to make my workflow
smoother and more efficient.

Included Configurations:
1. Neovim: Fine-tuned settings for powerful and efficient text editing.
2. Tmux: Customizations to enhance productivity using the terminal multiplexer.
3. Additional Tools: Various configurations for different tools used in my
   daily development tasks.

Feel free to explore and adapt these configurations to fit your preferences.
Whether you're a seasoned developer or just starting out, these dotfiles aim
to create a comfortable and productive environment for your software development journey.
